We're waiving change fees for more flexibility on certain tickets and travel dates.
Flexible travel updates , Opens in a new window

Face coverings and COVID-19 testing requirements

A face covering is required by federal law at the airport and on board American Airlines flights. In addition, passengers flying to the U.S. from another country, including U.S. citizens, must show proof of a negative COVID-19 test taken within 3 days of departure, or documentation of recovery. These rules do not apply to children under 2. Passengers who may be exempt from wearing a face covering due to a disability must contact us before travel.

Basic Economy

  • No changes allowed 1
  • Pay to choose any seat on American flights (or we'll assign seats at no charge during check-in) 2
  • Pay to check bags 3
  • Board in last group 3
  • No Elite Qualifying Credits (EQMs, EQSs or EQDs)

1 For flights booked on or after April 1, 2021.
2 Complimentary for AAdvantage® elite members based on status.
3 If you're an AAdvantage® elite status member or AAdvantage® credit cardholder, your bag benefit and boarding group applies if higher based on status.

Main Cabin

  • No change fees (difference in ticket price may apply)
  • Choose your seat at no charge on American flights (fee may apply for preferred or Main Cabin Extra seats)
  • 1 free checked bag 1
  • General boarding 1
  • Elite Qualifying Credits (EQMs, EQSs or EQDs)

1 If you're an AAdvantage® elite status member, your elite bag benefit and boarding group apply if higher based on status.

Premium Economy

  • No change fees (difference in ticket price may apply)
  • Wider seat with more legroom
  • 2 free checked bags
  • Priority security at participating airports
  • Priority boarding

Business

  • No change fees (difference in ticket price may apply)
  • Larger, more comfortable seat
  • 2 free checked bags*
  • Priority security at participating airports
  • Priority boarding

*AAdvantage Executive Platinum members get 1 extra checked bag.

First

  • No change fees (difference in ticket price may apply)
  • Our largest, most comfortable seat
  • 2 free checked bags *
  • Priority security at participating airports
  • Priority boarding

* On planes with both Business and First, you get 1 extra checked bag or 2 if you're AAdvantage Executive Platinum.
